creator: Sprint
descriptionHtml: Sprint MultiLine makes is easy to add a second company-managed number to a personal BYOD mobile phone.  Employees can now carry one phone while keeping their work and personal number completely separate.  The solution gives employees a distinct phone number for their work voice calls, text messaging and voicemail while maintaining their personal phone number.  The Sprint MultiLine app is simple to use and works over any domestic carrier network utilizing all communications channels: cellular voice, mobile data and WiFi.  Sprint MultiLine also provides granular insights and analytics into work related productivity.  Activation of the Sprint MultiLine service is required
descriptionShort: Easily add a 2nd company-managed number to a corporate or personal mobile phone.
